  "body": "Just like the setting to see only profile pictures from contacts, there exists the setting to only send your profile picture to your contacts.\r\nIn the status-go settings, it is called `profile-pictures-show-to`\r\n\r\nThe Nim code is already done here for the setting: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/4972/files#diff-037396a434984cbf3af28eb8f1bac61def03632f70e2f207fcfc7cae9fa60f08R64-R72\r\nYou only need to implement the QML code to get the setting and change it. \r\nI think the status-go code will then handle by itself if it should propagate your image.\r\n",
